# Chat Application

## Overview

This project is a front-end chat application that uses Ionic and Angular. Follow these instructions to set up and run the project.

## Prerequisites

1. **Node.js**
   - Download and install [Node.js](https://nodejs.org/).

2. **Ionic CLI**
   - Install the Ionic CLI globally using npm:
     ```bash
     npm install -g @ionic/cli
     ```

3. **Angular CLI**
   - Install the Angular CLI globally using npm:
     ```bash
     npm install -g @angular/cli
     ```

